snippet.title: Wonderbook: Diggs Nightcrawler Game Play
snippet.description:
See Diggs Nightcrawler in action with Wonderbook as your game controller.

For more information visit:
http://us.playstation.com/games/wonderbook-diggs-nightcrawler-ps3.html

Join Diggs Nightcrawler™ on a quest to clear his name and discover the true villain behind the crime in a filmnoir inspired, detective story for the whole family.
